## Standard Column Type
{{#if lang_ja}}
プロパティ`columnType`を利用して、列のタイプを指定できます。

|property|説明|LINK|
|---|---|---|
|指定なし|テキストをセルに描画します|---|
|number|数値をカンマ区切りでセルに描画します| [NumberColumn](./column_types/NumberColumn.html) |
|check|チェックボックスをセルに描画します|---|
|button|ボタンをセルに描画します| [ButtonColumn](./column_types/ButtonColumn.html) |
|image|画像をセルに描画します| [Draw Image](./draw_image.html) |
{{#if_v '0.3.0'}}
|multilinetext|複数行テキストをセルに描画します| [MultilineTextColumn](./column_types/MultilineTextColumn.html) |
{{/if_v}}
{{else}}
Set the column type by using `columnType`.

|property|description|LINK|
|---|---|---|
|none|draw text in the cell|---|
|number|draw number in the cell with comma-separated| [NumberColumn](./column_types/NumberColumn.html) |
|check|draw checkbox in the cell|---|
|button|draw button in the cell| [ButtonColumn](./column_types/ButtonColumn.html) |
|image|draw image in the cell| [Draw Image](./draw_image.html) |
{{#if_v '0.3.0'}}
|multilinetext|draw multiline text in the cell| [MultilineTextColumn](./column_types/MultilineTextColumn.html) |
{{/if_v}}
{{/if}}
{{/marked}}


